    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own cult, perform forbidden rituals, and crusade against the filthy non-believers. It's time to play god. CultGame is a retro cult simulator RPG where you start your own cult in a procedurally generated dark fantasy world with haunting ASCII art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/48313533770c8326e469c992ba3e93c3.avif?t=1762272037\" width=931 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and customize a cult, where beliefs serve as a system of perks and upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/64808be02136a1f021e8581604b1e8a1.gif?t=1762272037\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/64808be02136a1f021e8581604b1e8a1.poster.avif?t=1762272037\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/1bbc557111d3f5c365a55d5ca89e736d.avif?t=1762272037\" width=1406 height=325 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uniquely generated worlds with their own histories, characters, and factions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/d152a70603ce8c0a25bdacaca57c1d42.poster.avif?t=1762272037\" width=818 height=814 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/d152a70603ce8c0a25bdacaca57c1d42.webm?t=1762272037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/d152a70603ce8c0a25bdacaca57c1d42.mp4?t=1762272037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/5da988a955642a4bace19cce0d03aa93.avif?t=1762272037\" width=1521 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4X-strategy gameplay where you conquer the hearts and minds of citizens and insinuate your religion into government</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/e077aefee88db7d2896f6cd9988e8079.avif?t=1762272037\" width=824 height=722 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/6d864990592e6cdf33cfd33603640c5f.avif?t=1762272037\" width=1514 height=479 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of your cultists to go on missions for religious violence or to ask people out on dates</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/60e29510fb74d3632ce359e1da67110b.webp?t=1762272037\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/60e29510fb74d3632ce359e1da67110b.poster.avif?t=1762272037\" class=\"bb_img\" width=819 height=474 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/853ad61d602d41e044388c91896fd562.avif?t=1762272037\" width=1560 height=471 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perform rituals to give your cult an advantage toward its mission, such as summoning powerful units, or turning your foes inside out and exploding their tibia</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345980/extras/c23be78089c7b76709c46d6df37b6488.avif?t=1762272037\" width=826 height=646 /></span></p>",
